close_reason: "Implemented GH-207 audit evidence appends: --allow-audit-update now permits append-only --comment/--file/--doc evidence while lifecycle, dependency, test, note, learning, reminder/event, and clear/replace mutations remain restricted; tests, docs, coverage, temp smoke, dependency/security, Sentry, telemetry, and release-health checks completed."
body: "During a 3d-bots audit, pm update --allow-audit-update --comment/--file/--doc was rejected as restricted, forcing separate pm comments/files/docs calls. These are append-only non-lifecycle additions that match the audit-update intent. Permit them under --allow-audit-update (keep lifecycle/destructive flags restricted)."
